UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='A "Boarpocalypse," you say? These animals certainly have a unique idea of "Single combat!" No matter, you\'ve done well. With the quilboar in chaos I should have no trouble convincing the field commanders to execute any strays they find scurrying about. The General need not know we\'ve stepped up the campaign... it\'s for the better.' WHERE `word_id` = 176128; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25044
