UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='All my workers got driven straight out of the cavern here by those big swamp-lookin\' things! Darla\'s sent me here to pick up the pieces, but have you seen it in there? I ain\'t goin\' in!$B$BThere\'s a ton of explosives left behind that we can\'t just leave layin\' around$B$B I\'ll make you a deal: You run in there and get those explosives gathered up, and I will stay here and not get killed by swamp-things, and if you don\'t either, I\'ll pay ya! How\'s that sound?' WHERE `word_id` = 187875; -- locales_quest - details : entry=28340
