UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad that their spirits are now free. I wish we could say the same for the rest of their kind.$B$BThere is still much work to be done, especially elsewhere in Coilfang.' WHERE `word_id` = 191138; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29565
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad that you have come to me. For quite some time now I have been responsible for the training of our young $Cs, a responsibility that I intend to continue on this new world. I\'ve had my eye upon you for a while now and it would be my honor to help train you in the ways of the $C.$BShall we begin?' WHERE `word_id` = 146614; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9288
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad that you made it. Don\'t mind my new clothes. It seemed prudent to blend in.' WHERE `word_id` = 186974; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28124
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad to hear that it worked. The fewer the number of Nature\'s creatures that have to die, the better.$B$BWith all that you\'ve done for us already, I must say that I\'m beginning to grow very fond of your company.$B$BTake care, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 151275; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10506
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad to see that you have arrived safely in Nighthaven, $N. I offer you the welcome and the hospitality of the Cenarion Circle.' WHERE `word_id` = 183961; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27273
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad to see you received my message.' WHERE `word_id` = 187149; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28164
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad to see you\'ve come to your senses. Come and visit us in Zul\'Gurub sometime, $R. I\'ll be watching...' WHERE `word_id` = 180745; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26334
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad we were able to contain this before it spread across all of Zangarmarsh or further. Thank you.' WHERE `word_id` = 191233; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29614
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `word_id` = 164782; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14145
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Sunreavers.' WHERE `word_id` = 164761; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14112
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you managed to take care of, of... what did you say he called himself? Z\'kral?$B$BFrom your description, it sounds more like an \'it\' than a \'him\' but all that matters is it\'s dead.' WHERE `word_id` = 149639; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10099
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you were here, mon. Toshe be lookin\' like he wants to chase dem down. You should go help\'em.' WHERE `word_id` = 176559; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25164
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you\'re here, $C. Perhaps a seasoned veteran of the Horde\'s campaigns in Northrend and elsewhere can talk some sense into the Dragonmaw leadership...' WHERE `word_id` = 181419; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26539
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you\'ve arrived, $N. There are many things we will have to discuss, but more importantly is your training in the ways of the Light.$B$BThere are lessons all servants of the Light must learn. If you are ready, we\'ll begin discussing some of those now.' WHERE `word_id` = 140555; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=5634
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C. These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `word_id` = 171924; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27307
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you\'ve proven you can follow orders. If I had a copper piece for every arrogant fool in shiny armor to come here and think they\'re above the chain of command... well, I\'d have a few gold.$B$BNow that you\'ve demonstrated a measure of discipline, I have other tasks more suitable for someone of your caliber.' WHERE `word_id` = 156120; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11270
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad you\'ve returned safely, $N. While it may not look like it now, you\'ve proven to be a tremendous asset in the protection of Anvilmar. Here, take this as a symbol of my gratitude.' WHERE `word_id` = 165838; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=218
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m going to miss you, $N. I owe you such a debt of gratitude; I think I\'ll never be able to repay it.$B$BI hope that you enjoy your new head and chest armor, and that it protects you for a long time to come.' WHERE `word_id` = 144784; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8999
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m happy for Nathaniel: he\'s spent so long trying to return to Northridge, and now with the Scarlet Crusade out of the way, he can finally move back home. It\'s just... even for such a seemingly-idyllic setting, it\'s not really the best place to raise a family.$B$BFor example: along this valley\'s edge, you will find rabid foxes searching for innocent prey. Every once in a while I catch a glimpse of one looking right at me.$B$BPlease, $C, remove some of these foxes. I don\'t feel safe with them near.' WHERE `word_id` = 183154; -- locales_quest - details : entry=27013
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m happy you\'re seeing the error of your ways, $N. Keep the supplies coming; we\'re not going to forget about you so easily, $Gmister:miss;!' WHERE `word_id` = 145315; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9267
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m heartened to have the Breath of Cenarius back where it belongs and I know the rest of the circle will be impressed by your efforts. You may have also set back the plans of the Twilight\'s Hammer clan a bit, too. Excellent work.' WHERE `word_id` = 187892; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28343
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m honored that the warchief chose me to craft a weapon for you, $N. With such exotic materials, it will be a very fine bow.' WHERE `word_id` = 184349; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27395
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m impressed by the cleverness of our new goblin allies, but I\'m even more impressed by you, $N. Look at the gaze of terror frozen onto the Captain\'s face! He never saw your attack coming. Imagine the fear this will cause in Northwatch when they see what happened to one of their precious officers in night elf lands. Well done, $C. Our assault proceeds...' WHERE `word_id` = 174435; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14464
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m impressed that you managed to survive the carnage. You just might be the person we need for a dangerous mission.' WHERE `word_id` = 151640; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10595
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m impressed you are standing here, $N. Many an apprentice has perished to the voidwalker, or even the voidstone itself.$B$BThe voidwalker is now yours to command. Use your new servant well.' WHERE `word_id` = 147713; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9619
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m impressed, $C, but there\'s no time to lose. I will give you your next task, because you will still need to acquire a few more important components before we can proceed.$B$BSpeak to me again when you feel that you are ready for the challenge that lies ahead.' WHERE `word_id` = 144665; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8961
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m impressed, $N. And I\'m not the type who\'s easily impressed.' WHERE `word_id` = 156666; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11466
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m impressed. I never thought I would see an icemaw matriarch again. Especially not one this size.' WHERE `word_id` = 162083; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12983
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m in your debt, mon. Take this as payment.' WHERE `word_id` = 158858; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12176
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m indebted to you, $C. At least with most of the mules and equipment recovered, we can hope to rebuild our numbers soon.$B$BPlease, take this.' WHERE `word_id` = 155371; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11224
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m just looking over my paperwork here, and it says that we were expecting a FEMALE $R $C. You\'re not, umm... Never mind. It would appear that you are not the person that I originally hired, but you did a good job. So I\'m going to pay you anyhow.' WHERE `word_id` = 183669; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27156
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m looking forward to fighting with you.' WHERE `word_id` = 186131; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27891
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m Maxx Avalanche, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to perform a Primal Strike. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn it from me and then go use it on a training dummy to the southeast.' WHERE `word_id` = 173105; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14011
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m much obliged, $C. This\'ll go a ways towards getting my family back on their feet.' WHERE `word_id` = 178984; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25856
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m not at all surprised that a warlock like you fought your way out of Gnomeregan. Few people, even among the gnomes, truly understand the nature of the power we wield.$B$BLet me show you a conjuration that I find handy. This spell, called Immolate, sets your target aflame, causing damage immediately and over time. Use it well, $N, and your enemies will come to fear you.' WHERE `word_id` = 180235; -- locales_quest - details : entry=26201
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m not sure that I like the sound of that one bit! The Lich King absconding with Ymiron can only mean trouble. Unfortunate that you weren\'t able to kill him along with his queen.$B$BStill, you\'ve put a huge dent in their plans and bought us the valuable time that we need.$B$BAnd who knows, with the way you get around, you\'ll likely run into King Ymiron again. I\'m sure that he won\'t fare so well the next time you meet.' WHERE `word_id` = 156620; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11452
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m not sure what I\'m going to do with all of these. I\'ll probably fence them and donate the proceeds to the Stormwind orphanage. Now to find someone sick enough to buy such a thing. It\'ll probably be a goblin. Or, a gnome warlock.' WHERE `word_id` = 185267; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27652
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m not surprised to see you\'re such a quick study. I look forward to showing you more of our tricks of the trade.' WHERE `word_id` = 180259; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26207
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m not what you\'d call "very strong" or "battle-hardened", but I get the job done my own way. Lookin\' forward to fightin\' with you. I never fought with a fancy-lookin\' $C before.' WHERE `word_id` = 185925; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27828
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m pleased to report that our brand recognition in this area has skyrocketed now that you\'ve killed most of the people who didn\'t want us here.' WHERE `word_id` = 175656; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24927
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m pleased, $N. That was quicker than I expected.' WHERE `word_id` = 180920; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26381
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m really sorry about this, $R. He\'s always getting himself into trouble. I just wish I could put a leash on him...' WHERE `word_id` = 276204; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9923
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m Sister Goldskimmer, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to cast Flash Heal. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn it from me and then use it to heal the injured employees around the courtyard.' WHERE `word_id` = 173097; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14009
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m Slinky Sharpshiv, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to perform an Eviscerate. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn the ability from me and then go practice it on a training dummy in the southeast corner of the courtyard.' WHERE `word_id` = 173101; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14010
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m starting to respect your prowess in the ring, $N. Now I really don\'t like you.$B$BI would much rather have preferred to see you and your friends stuck to the bottom of that flesh giant\'s foot!' WHERE `word_id` = 163078; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13217
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m sure she deserved it, $N. She should never have betrayed you like that. It gives me the shivers to think that she might have kissed that monster, the Trade Prince!' WHERE `word_id` = 176866; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25243
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m sure Sylvanas will be glad to have that problem taken care of, $N. The task I gave you wasn\'t easy, but here you stand, victorious. That commands respect, and what you\'ve done won\'t be forgotten.' WHERE `word_id` = 164912; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14355
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m sure that only worked because the troggs aren\'t bright to begin with. But then again, us dwarves were once creatures of the earth as well.$B$BBeing bossed around by a kobold doesn\'t sound quite dignified, and I\'m glad we didn\'t get to find out if they could pull that off.' WHERE `word_id` = 182541; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26846
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m sure the first thing you learned was how unsympathetic the crawler was during the bonding process. It\'s all claws until they know you aren\'t there to throw them into a boiling pot.' WHERE `word_id` = 147610; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9591
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m sure the old boy must\'ve seen his days coming to an end. With all these new arrivals, the old order couldn\'t stand. It\'s just as well his spirit is at rest now.' WHERE `word_id` = 148871; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9903
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m sure you are up to the task I have for you if you\'ve made it this far in one piece. Between you and me, you may want to enjoy yourself in the Grim Guzzler while you\'re there. It could be the last drink you ever have.' WHERE `word_id` = 184956; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27569
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m surprised to see Huntsman Markhor working with me for once. He\'s usually quite stubborn. He does tend to a strong hatred for magic, though. I hope you do, too, $C, because we\'re going to strip the Scarlet Crusade of theirs.' WHERE `word_id` = 183046; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26987
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m tempted to keep it for myself and return my client\'s money. It could certainly expand the reach of my business.$B$B<The wind trader sighs.>$B$BHowever, I have a reputation to uphold.$B$BSpeaking of my reputation, thank you for helping me to maintain it. Here is your commission.$B$BCome back tomorrow and I will have another request for you to fulfill.' WHERE `word_id` = 154281; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11386
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m trying to decide at which I\'m more surprised... that you actually came to the aid of a Black Dragon or that you\'re still in one piece after speaking with Nalice.$B$BHer words drip venom, but I suppose Wyrmrest can keep even our kind in check sometimes.$B$BOr perhaps it\'s just the armies of the red dragonflight that are massed around her.' WHERE `word_id` = 159718; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12447
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'m very glad there were some to be saved... with luck, they\'ll make it back to Rainspeaker Canopy safely.' WHERE `word_id` = 160321; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12580
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve actually nearly perfected my dream machine: The Skystrider! The world\'s first flying Mechanostrider! But, well�$B$BWhen I was putting the finishing touches on it in my secret cavern lab, my other creations became, er, jealous. Giving mechanical birds a personality to begin with was probably a bad idea, but that\'s already done.$B$BI need the Supermechanical Robo-Widget from the original Skystrider if I want to rebuild it! Please, journey into the cave and retrieve it for me!' WHERE `word_id` = 183227; -- locales_quest - details : entry=27032
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve already spoken with several orcs that have returned from the beach. All of them told me that you were the one who saved them. You\'ve done a noble task today, $N. Lok\'tar ogar!  For the Horde!' WHERE `word_id` = 176625; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25179
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve asked the impossible of you, yet I expect you to succeed. Much depends on it.' WHERE `word_id` = 151086; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10445
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been expecting you! This inn is part of Sunreaver\'s Sanctuary, the Horde\'s enclave in Dalaran.$B$BDon\'t forget to bind your hearthstone here for easy travel to the city and access to the portal to Orgrimmar, out by the fountain.' WHERE `word_id` = 191225; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29609
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been expecting you, $C. We have much work to do, you and I.' WHERE `word_id` = 158093; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11995
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been expecting you, $N. Do not be alarmed. My name is Belrysa. I am a priestess of the moon... a night elf. You might not know my people, but the destinies of our two races have been linked since the Curse befell you.' WHERE `word_id` = 175012; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24578
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been expecting you, $R. I saw your spirit fly by and sensed the mystic watching behind your eyes.$B$BYour fate and that of the Kalu\'ak are now tied together.' WHERE `word_id` = 158213; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12030
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 182604; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26865
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been informed there\'s a bear warning active for the woodlands as well! They love those stabthistle seeds.$B$BIt\'s a good thing you gathered those so they don\'t attract more bears!' WHERE `word_id` = 183197; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27025
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been instructed to prepare you for battle. Though, from the look of you, it looks like you\'ve already spent a little time out in the field. Good.$B$BIt\'s been said that a warriors fight not only with their arms but their legs. You must learn to move quickly around the battlefield .$B$BSpeak to me again, and I will teach you how to charge.' WHERE `word_id` = 176496; -- locales_quest - details : entry=25147
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been told that I\'m supposed to train you how to be a hunter. That\'s all well and good, but in my opinion, you\'ll get more training out in the field than you will talking about theories with me.$B$BI suppose I can show you a couple of my tricks. Here, come take a look at this...' WHERE `word_id` = 175825; -- locales_quest - details : entry=24964
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve been trying to impress our new Horde allies with our legendary Goblin efficiency, but in hindsight automating the shredders was a bad idea. Now they\'re mindless killing machines, rampaging over the countryside. Don\'t get me wrong - that kind of thing has its place - but for the time being I need a brave $C to help me get these things under control.$B$BIt\'s easy. Automated shredders, like all machines, must first be beaten into submission. Afterwards, seize the controls and I\'ll radio you instructions.' WHERE `word_id` = 173365; -- locales_quest - details : entry=14129
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve brought you back from the brink of death, hero! Deathwing is upon us! We need your help.' WHERE `word_id` = 184294; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27377
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve chained the wretch to the post over there and I\'ll look into getting my hands on more of them.$B$BNow lets make some use of that eye.' WHERE `word_id` = 162765; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13143
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve found them, $R. The Scourge. How I\'ve longed for this day.' WHERE `word_id` = 184260; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27370
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve got a great one for you this time, $N. We\'re gonna initiate these ogres into the Horde...working directly under us.' WHERE `word_id` = 175599; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24905
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve got to admit, the spell I just taught you probably won\'t increase your intellect severalfold. That was a lie to get you to buy my services. But it will still be a helpful spell for you and your allies. No hard feelings!' WHERE `word_id` = 175831; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24965
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve got to hand it to you, $N. Our odds might not be the best, but I feel a lot better with you lending a hand.' WHERE `word_id` = 163958; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13611
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve heard about your help in clearing out some of the orcs. You\'ve shown that you can handle yourself in combat.$B$BI want to show you a new skill. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.' WHERE `word_id` = 182762; -- locales_quest - details : entry=26917
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve heard enough, $N. We must make sure whatever\'s happening at Silverbrook doesn\'t spread to the rest of the continent.$B$BI don\'t care if it\'s the water, the altitude or an ancient troll curse that\'s driven these villagers murderously insane... return to Silverbrook and put an end to them.' WHERE `word_id` = 158546; -- locales_quest - details : entry=12103
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve heard much about you, $N. You have a bright future ahead of you in the Horde.' WHERE `word_id` = 184016; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27298
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve heard much of your contributions to the Horde, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 184043; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27304
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve heard your name whispered from the shadows, $N. It\'s said that you\'re looking for someone experienced to show you the ropes - someone like me. I can do that, but it\'ll cost you a small cut of your take every time I\'ve got something to teach you. So yes, I will train you in what it means to be a rogue.$B$BBut remember, if you ever get caught stealing something, this conversation never took place. Now get out there and show me what you\'re made of!' WHERE `word_id` = 146826; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9392
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve never received something like this before. How lovely!' WHERE `word_id` = 144506; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8899
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve not seen a finer display of $C prowess.' WHERE `word_id` = 176055; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25024
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve put Vardmadra aside for the moment. She\'s someplace safe until we can enact our final revenge!' WHERE `word_id` = 162734; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13137
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve scouted all over these highlands, $N, and there\'s one thing I\'ve found I haven\'t been able to explain.$B$BTo the northeast of here, there\'s a circle of stones, like the others you\'ll find everythwhere in Arathi... but the largest and most imposing of them, built into the mountainside itself.$B$BJust between you and me, I heard voices while I was there. Whispers of the earth. If you\'re the curious type, you could go see for yourself...' WHERE `word_id` = 180771; -- locales_quest - details : entry=26341
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='I\'ve seen the insignia on this scroll before during my time in Northrend. You say this was on that crone who leads the pigs in Razorfen Kraul?$B$BI\'ll be damned if I\'m going to let the Scourge get a foothold here. The one who wrote this - this Malcin - is one of the Lich King\'s servants, obviously, and that makes him a target. Your target.$B$BThey\'re not going to take Kalimdor.' WHERE `word_id` = 164908; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14352
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Iain sent ya? You don\'t look like a Firebeard to me. Why exactly should I be listenin\' to anything you say?' WHERE `word_id` = 185840; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27807
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Icecrown Scourge slain' WHERE `word_id` = 164054; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=13671
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Icefist, eh? I\'ve heard his name before. Dat\'s some good work, mon. Hopefully we Darkspear can turn our attention back to dat dragon menace now.' WHERE `word_id` = 158723; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12145
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Icemaw Matriarch Rescued' WHERE `word_id` = 162085; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=12983
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Iceskin Sentry destroyed' WHERE `word_id` = 162855; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=13160
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Icy Ghouls Exploded' WHERE `word_id` = 163301; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=13264
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If a tree falls in the forest, and you can\'t hear it through the saw blade, does it really make a sound?' WHERE `word_id` = 158308; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12050
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If Anchorite Ahuurn counts you a friend, then you may prove trustworthy. Please forgive my wariness, $R, but it is often all that stands between my people and death. You are welcome to shelter among us, and perhaps our mutual trust will grow.' WHERE `word_id` = 148319; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9776
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If Gnomeregan Covert Operations is recommending you, then you must have made quite an impression. Your help will be most welcome here, as we\'ve a wealth of enemies and few enough mountaineers to face them.' WHERE `word_id` = 180888; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26373
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If he still lives, I may be able to locate this poor soul.' WHERE `word_id` = 178119; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25638
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If I could still breathe I\'d let out a sigh of relief. Don\'t get too comfortable, though, $N, your mission here has just begun.' WHERE `word_id` = 184129; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27333
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If I had any reservations regarding your commitment when you first arrived, I no longer have any. With just a little more effort you could be a permanent member of my operation.' WHERE `word_id` = 161753; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12907
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If I hadn\'t seen you kill a few of the mangy things with my own eyes, I\'d think you did not complete the task I asked of you. It looks like we\'re hardly putting a dent in their numbers.' WHERE `word_id` = 175672; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24930
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If I remember correctly, Azure Watch\'s hippogryph master is Zaldaan. If you\'ve spoken to him before, then you can take one of my hippogryphs to him.$B$BThat\'s a good lesson to know: hippogryphs are always trained to fly to their capital city, but they\'ll only take you to a remote hippogryph master after you\'ve already been there.$B$BSince you arrived on one of Zaldaan\'s hippogryphs, you can also use that route to return to Azure Watch with the caregiver\'s supplies.' WHERE `word_id` = 168945; -- locales_quest - details : entry=9606
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If I survive my wounds, I will always remember your name, $C.$B$BWhenever the wind whistles through the trees, I will always hear your name.$B$BThank you.' WHERE `word_id` = 189345; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28831
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If it weren\'t you saying it, I wouldn\'t believe what that troublesome goblin has to say. This is troubling indeed, but I think our Earthen Ring friends have a few ideas.$B$BAnd now that you\'re here....' WHERE `word_id` = 179497; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25984
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If it\'s Dunwalds you be lookin\' for, it\'s Dunwalds you\'ve found. A couple of\'m anyway. I can\'t find me other brothers for the life of me.' WHERE `word_id` = 185213; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27640
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If Leyara bore witness to the War of the Shifting Sands, then it seems likely she knew Fandral - and his late son, Valstann - far more closely than any of us suspected.$B$BIt would seem that your journey does not end here, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 190691; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29302
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If Malfurion placed his trust in you, then so shall I. You\'ll find that our enemies greatly outnumber us this far south.$B$BWhere brute force and numbers fail us, strategy and guile will prove our biggest advantages.' WHERE `word_id` = 172766; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13902
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If my calculations are correct - and they\'re often not - you\'re gonna need about 10-20 seaforium depth charges.$B$BOh yea, you\'ll be planting these mothers into their sinkholes.' WHERE `word_id` = 156998; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11606
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If not for you, I would surely be on my way back to Stormwind to be paraded as a trophy and a slave. The Alliance dogs found me unconscious on the shore and put me in this magical cage. It was keeping me from connecting with the elements. No longer!' WHERE `word_id` = 173638; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14242
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If nothin\' else, you bought us some time, and some room to open up our supply lines through this siege. Yer a fine $C.' WHERE `word_id` = 186627; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28028
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If only we could have saved him.' WHERE `word_id` = 191275; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=29652
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If the great Malfurion requires my presence, it is my duty to heed his call. It is also my duty to protect these ruins, however.$B$BPerhaps you\'ll help me fulfill both my obligations, $N?' WHERE `word_id` = 172227; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13579
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If the old draenei said to destroy the book, why didn\'t you?$B$B<Ramdor glares at you.>$B$BBah, what\'s the difference. You might be greedy but at least you\'re honest.$B$BMe on the other hand... I lied to get this book. I have no idea where these poor lost souls kept their treasure nor would I tell you if I did - however - I do have something for you. You did a good thing on this day. Perhaps a great thing... You should be rewarded.$B$BBy the way, welcome to the fold.$B$B<Ramdor points to the spirits.>' WHERE `word_id` = 150293; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10253
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If there is only one lesson you deign to remember from your time on Sunstrider Isle, let it be this - control your thirst for magic. It is a thirst unending, $N - you must absorb energy to survive via Mana Tap, and you must control how you release it via Arcane Torrent. Failure is to become one of the Wretched... hopelessly addicted and insane.$B$BSeek out creatures on the isle that have mana and Mana Tap them. Learn to master your cravings of power. When you have sufficiently fed, return to me.' WHERE `word_id` = 145965; -- locales_quest - details : entry=8346
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If this does not freeze the blood in their veins, nothing will. You have done the Mag\'har justice, $N. And for justice, Mag\'har rewards greatly.' WHERE `word_id` = 148891; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9907
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If this is the same Drakuru from Drak\'Tharon Keep we are going to need... outside assistance.$B$BDeath knights of Acherus are stationed nearby, undoubtedly following the same trail of Scourge destruction that lead the Argent Crusade here. As half of our army is tied up at the Argent Stand, battling crazed Drakkari trolls, we will have to join forces with the Knights of the Ebon Blade.$B$B<Lantinga mutters under his breath.>$B$BI was hoping I\'d never have to see those scoundrels again after Light\'s Hope...' WHERE `word_id` = 161649; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12883
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If this is what it appears to be, the Forsaken have some explaining to do!$B$BThe antics of the Grimtotems have long tried the Warchief\'s patience. We have traditionally treated it as a matter to be settled among the tauren people, but this letter may change it.$B$BIt will take time to investigate these suspicions, but do not speak to anyone of what you have seen this day.' WHERE `word_id` = 153982; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11186
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If we can get things straightened out here, we have a chance to strike at the Alliance while most of their forces are busy in the Barrens.' WHERE `word_id` = 188562; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28554
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you are hungry, then you have come to the right place my friend!$B$BDumplings are the traditional food of the Lunar Festival; it has been served since the time of the first Lunar Festival, and I am pleased to be able to offer it at this one. In exchange for just a single coin of ancestry, I will share with you a sampling of one of the tastiest dishes you will ever enjoy!' WHERE `word_id` = 272146; -- locales_quest - details : entry=8863
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you are prepared to leave Camp Narache behind, I will help call the spirits to guide you onwards.' WHERE `word_id` = 174542; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=23733
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you ever get tired of your being a $C, come look me up. You seem very good with those fleshy hands of yours.' WHERE `word_id` = 181632; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26591
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you truly dislike your present, you can exchange it for gold by speaking to a Smokeywood Pastures merchant.$B$BAll exchanges are final.' WHERE `word_id` = 190797; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=29382
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you trust him, talk to Baron Longshore to free him from his manacles.' WHERE `word_id` = 337683; -- locales_quest - CompletedText : entry=14046
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you want to become a stronger warrior, you\'ll need to work on your weapons. You\'ll find stronger swords and larger shields out on your adventures, that I have no doubt about. However, as a warrior you also shouldn\'t forget your legs. $B$BTrain with me, $N, and I\'ll show you how to move quickly around the battlefield. You care to learn?' WHERE `word_id` = 175845; -- locales_quest - details : entry=24969
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you want to really demonstrate your bravery to me, let me send you after something that really bites. The savannah huntresses of the Barrens are as sly as they come. Tough, resourceful, quick... and deadly. They\'ve been hassling our scouts recently around the outskirts of the town, especially to the northeast.$B$BBe wary as you hunt them, $N, or you may find yourself no longer the predator, but instead the prey.' WHERE `word_id` = 166651; -- locales_quest - details : entry=903
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you\'d like to learn to cook Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, I can help. If you\'re not already a cook, all you have to do is train and you\'ll be cooking in no time!' WHERE `word_id` = 164592; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14022
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='If you\'d like to learn to cook Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, I can help. If you\'re not already a cook, all you have to do is train and you\'ll be cooking in no time.' WHERE `word_id` = 164621; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14036
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Ilthalaine sent you? He was wise to do so. I am indeed in need of help.' WHERE `word_id` = 189135; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28734
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Images of a great and distant tree flood your mind. Your stomach lurches as you reorient the stone, briefly filling your senses with visions of a fiery portal, a towering mountain, a frigid wasteland, and a terrible scar across the earth. After a moment, the magical energies of the stone calm, and you feel you are but a step away from Valormok. Andorel\'s invasion can begin...' WHERE `word_id` = 174563; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24434
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Immolate tested on Captured Northwatch Scout' WHERE `word_id` = 176495; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=25146
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Immolated Supplicant saved' WHERE `word_id` = 177136; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=25330
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impeccable timing. Like clockwork! Trouble comes. You come. Save the day. Clockwork! We\'ve devised our brilliant plan. Gloriously simple, barring the hostility of local life. Simpler yet with a you available!' WHERE `word_id` = 179150; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25893
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Imperean gave you a primal essence of herself? I can hear its howling winds!$B$BI know a ritual we can make use of it in. We must hurry before her primal rips itself apart!' WHERE `word_id` = 157115; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11629
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Imperial Eagle\'s sight bound' WHERE `word_id` = 159737; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=12453
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impossible... Father, is it you?! You have done me a great service, hero. I offer you the reins of my faithful steed. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `word_id` = 275300; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24915
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive - your victory in Zul\'Gurub has assured us - nay, the world - that Hakkar will not prevail. The time may come when you face the Blood God directly... and should this come to pass know that your reverence is assured amongst the Zandalar tribe.$B$BOh, and this simple robe should help out too I think.$B$B<Al\'tabim winks knowingly at you.>' WHERE `word_id` = 142877; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8077
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive work, laddie. We can hold the perimeter from here on out. Here, take this for yer troubles. It might come in handy, as I\'ve got something more important to ask of ye...' WHERE `word_id` = 174683; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24469
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, $C. Are you certain you\'re not a member of the expedition?$B$BNo, I\'m certain of it. There would\'ve been a crash joke in there somewhere.' WHERE `word_id` = 160181; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12551
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, $N. It would seem that you are capable enough to handle yourself. Perhaps a more suitable challenge could be found for one of your abilities.' WHERE `word_id` = 181983; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26688
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, $N. Very impressive. You embody all of the strength of the Wolf Ancient, and possess the wisdom to use your powers well. I salute you.' WHERE `word_id` = 177196; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25354
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, fleshling. You are far more capable than I initially assumed.$B$BI will extend that sentiment to the Stonemother as well.' WHERE `word_id` = 181880; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26659
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, little one. You have gone through much trouble to gain the favor of the Bronze Flight. Your dedication is noted.$B$BThe signet ring of the conqueror will greatly enhance your physical attacks.$B$BBe warned, once you have chosen your path, you will have no recourse should you change your mind.' WHERE `word_id` = 144249; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8752
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, little one. You have gone through much trouble to gain the favor of the Bronze Flight. Your dedication is noted.$B$BThe signet ring of the invoker will greatly enhance your magical and natural abilities.$B$BBe warned, once you have chosen your path, you will have no recourse should you change your mind.' WHERE `word_id` = 144253; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8757
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, little one. You have gone through much trouble to gain the favor of the Bronze Flight. Your dedication is noted.$B$BThe signet ring of the protector will offer superior protection against the forces of evil.$B$BBe warned, once you have chosen your path, you will have no recourse should you change your mind.' WHERE `word_id` = 144241; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8747
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, mon! Fate be kind in bringin\' us together.$B$BSoon I be avengin\' me bruddas by cleansin\' Drak\'Tharon, and you be awarded Drak\'Tharon\'s greatest treasure.' WHERE `word_id` = 161278; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12802
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive, valiant. I will make the arrangements for your test immediately.' WHERE `word_id` = 164135; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13697
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive. I hope my huntress carried her weight. If we continue with this fervor, we may yet still free Teldrassil from the corruption that Alexstrasza herself could not burn out.' WHERE `word_id` = 172877; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=13945
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive. I wasn\'t expecting a mere mortal to prove as worthy an ally as you.$B$BI fear our efforts have not been sufficient, however. The Scourge shows no signs of stopping.' WHERE `word_id` = 160479; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12620
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive. Most impressive.$B$BYou\'ve got potential, kid. Now I\'m going to give you the chance to have some real fun!' WHERE `word_id` = 148662; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9850
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive... you have accomplished today what few thought was possible. Your reverence in the tribe is assured for a lifetime, $N. You have earned the right to don the madcap\'s tunic - do so with our blessing.' WHERE `word_id` = 142859; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8073
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impressive... you\'ve successfully collected the required Paragons of Power, $N. Your accomplishments in Zul\'Gurub for the Zandalar are legendary; hence forth, you\'ll be revered amongst the tribe. Here is your tunic, mighty $C!' WHERE `word_id` = 142819; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=8065
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Imprisoned Soldiers Released' WHERE `word_id` = 179127; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=25888
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Imprisoned Warriors Freed' WHERE `word_id` = 179574; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=26008
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Imps are creatures of deception. With so many of them spotted at Shadowlurk Ridge, I\'m positive something is being hidden there. Our little friend will tell us exactly how to find it... if he doesn\'t want to go back in the sack.' WHERE `word_id` = 186556; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=28000
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Imps terrified' WHERE `word_id` = 187670; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=28288
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Impsy captured' WHERE `word_id` = 186557; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText1 : entry=28000
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In a round-about way, R-3D0 has informed you that if you follow the trail of spare parts up the ramp here to the Razor Ridge, you will find the gnomes at a place named Toshley\'s Station.$B$BIf you find him, speak with Toshley.' WHERE `word_id` = 151576; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=10581
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In all my days of living I would have never expected to see this...$B$B<Father Montoy appears to be salivating.>$B$BOh yes, you will be rewarded dear $G. You will be greatly rewarded. Give it here. Now!' WHERE `word_id` = 272257; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9120
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In her memories, Leyara spoke of Malfurion. The tragedies of her past - at least, in her opinion - are largely due to his actions.$B$BMalfurion must remember Leyara from before she became a druid of the flame. You resolve to bring the locket to him in the Firelands. Hopefully he can answer any remaining questions.' WHERE `word_id` = 190718; -- locales_quest - details : entry=29311
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In life, Gorefiend was a bastard, but in death, Gorefiend was an unmitigated terror.$B$BTo the southeast you will find Netherwing Ledge. What was once part of the mainland of Shadowmoon is now a floating island in the sky.$B$BVhel\'kur, spawn of Deathwing, once called it his home, but now knows it as his grave. He flies an endless circle above the island, seething at his defeat to Gorefiend.$B$BIf you are to recover the Gorefiend\'s armor, it is Vhel\'kur that you must defeat.' WHERE `word_id` = 151790; -- locales_quest - details : entry=10634
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In order to fly to a town, you must have already been there and spoken with the wind rider master of that town. You have been to the Bloodhoof Village and spoken to their wind rider master Tak, so for a small fee you can take a wind rider to him from here.$B$BSpeak with me again when you are ready. Once at Bloodhoof Village, you can then deliver the leather goods to Varg Whisperwind.' WHERE `word_id` = 168033; -- locales_quest - details : entry=6364
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In order to have great cuisine, you need to have great ingredients. And these eggs look great!$B$BI\'ve just finished cleaning off my frying pan, so you\'re more than welcome to join me for a meal!' WHERE `word_id` = 146700; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9349
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In order to prove yourself to the Mok\'Nathal, Leoroxx has ordered you to slay Gnosh Brognat, leader of the ogres at the Bladespire Outpost. Return to Leoroxx at Mok\'Nathal Village in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains after you have done so, or do not return at all.' WHERE `word_id` = 152574; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=10843
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In sparing the land further suffering, you\'ve also helped us soothe the Greenwarden. Many thanks, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 179350; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25939
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In the earth, my brothers can grant life anew. You have saved them from a fate far worse than death.$B$BI don\'t know a word in your tongue that could express how much this means to my kind. Thank you, $R.' WHERE `word_id` = 159603; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12417
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In their folly, the Argent Crusade has chosen to turn a blind eye upon the presence of the Scarlet Onslaught. We will not.$B$BWe do not care if they might assist in the battle against the Lich King. We do not believe them worthy of existence. We will be their end, once and for all!' WHERE `word_id` = 161300; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12807
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In this, we deny Deathwing the destruction that he so passionately seeks. In this, life continues.' WHERE `word_id` = 184735; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=27506
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In time, we\'ll have to devise a plan for returning the species to its native state, but for now, periodically culling their numbers is about the best we can hope for. Thank you for your help, $N.' WHERE `word_id` = 147841; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9647
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In times of crisis, a desperate act may be all that is needed to secure victory. Sending a swarm of kobolds at the enemy may be the edge that we need to win.' WHERE `word_id` = 179763; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=26066
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='In your future as a mage, you\'ll be expected to master a wide variety of spells. In fact, I want to teach you one right now. It\'s called Arcane Missiles and it allows you to throw volleys of arcane energy at your opponent. However, you won\'t be able to use it all the time. Each time you cast a spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll trigger an opportunity to use the missiles.$B$BI want you to try out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site.' WHERE `word_id` = 182972; -- locales_quest - details : entry=26968
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Inactive Fel Reaver Destroyed' WHERE `word_id` = 152633; -- locales_quest - ObjectiveText3 : entry=10855
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Incapable fools. I begin to wonder if any of these louts from the tournament will be of any use at all. Perhaps you\'ll prove me wrong.' WHERE `word_id` = 165129; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24682
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Inconceivably immaculate! This device stores Light energy at levels beyond those of any source yet known! Oh, the possible applications shiver my whiskers and curl my toes. Ho ho! The anti-nocturnal photo-dispersement geno-actuator I could build with this would turn dusk into dawn! The Scourge won\'t know what hit them. We\'ll destroy them all in one pull of a lever!' WHERE `word_id` = 161305; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12809
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Incredible work, $N! My men report a breakthrough. Their stronghold won\'t survive much longer...' WHERE `word_id` = 176276; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25081
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Incredible! Did you find any survivors?$B$B<Achelus lowers his voice to a whisper.>$B$BI\'ll be honest, $N; nobody else was willing to take on this mission. You are a brave $C...' WHERE `word_id` = 147878; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9669
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Incredible! Let me just say that I continue to be amazed by what you younger races seem capable of.$B$BWe are indebted to you. Will you come back and help us again tomorrow?' WHERE `word_id` = 159568; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=12372
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Incredible! This was all part of their master plan!$B$BThis information must reach the king and your own leaders. The implications are staggering.' WHERE `word_id` = 147395; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=9537
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Incredible! What could those iron menaces be up to? What are they doing in the Storm Peaks? And what is this Loken!? I\'ll forward this information to our central base of operations in the Dragonblight, $N. I\'ll also let \'em know that you were invaluable in the acquisition of said info.' WHERE `word_id` = 156766; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11495
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Indeed, I fear my customer will not have time to peruse the entirety of this book. Nevertheless, that is not our concern. Here is your reward.$B$BCome back tomorrow and I will have another request for you to fulfill.' WHERE `word_id` = 154201; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11370
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Indeed, I have spoken to Corithras on my way here, and he has gifted me with the waters you have been gathering. They may well prove useful sooner than we\'d imagined. Strangely, the growing corruption we\'ve felt is actually a good sign. Teldrassil has been burdened with this taint for a long time, and thanks to the blessing of the dragon aspects, only now is it coming to the surface in a form that we might strike against.' WHERE `word_id` = 166708; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=933
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Indeed, if the orcs never make it to Azeroth, the Alliance will never form. Eventually civil war will break out, further weakening the human kingdoms.$B$BUltimately the Burning Legion will invade Azeroth, destroying it in the absence of any defenders.' WHERE `word_id` = 150493; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10296
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Indeed, it must have been a difficult struggle, $C. I feel greatly relieved now that he will not be breathing down our necks here.$B$BI will send this skull down to Chort for safekeeping. I\'m beginning to think that with your help, we might just pull this off.' WHERE `word_id` = 153234; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=10995
