UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='YES?! Do you see me interrupting your fascinating argument? No... no, please, go ahead. I\'m sure that your interruption is about something very important. More important than dealing with the survival of everyone here, in fact.' WHERE `word_id` = 177601; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=25488
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Yesssssss!  We will slay the Kvaldir\'s beast!  I will show these brutes to never cross a priestess of the scale!' WHERE `word_id` = 157095; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=11625
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc3`='Yet again, vengeance slips through my grasp. It\'s hard to believe how much stronger he\'s gotten.$B$BIt was foolish of you to come for me, but it\'s good to know that there are still some champions of the Horde that aren\'t useless cowards. The information Uther gave us may well be key to finally killing Arthas, though it is becoming more and more clear that the Horde will not be able to accomplish this on their own.$B$BGo, $C. I expect your prowess may be needed again very soon.' WHERE `word_id` = 165182; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=24802
